<HEADLINE> Arafat Calls on Israel to Abide by Agreements </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, June 29 (Xinhua) -- Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat
Tuesday called on Israeli Prime Minister-elect Ehud Barak to
comply with all agreements Israel signed with the Palestinians
and to stop settlement activities in the occupied territories.
</P>
<P>
