this bold step," it said.
</P>
<P>
It said the action plan which was being prepared by the IMF
would provide the framework to implement the Zimbabwe Program for
Economic and Social Transformation and turn the economy back to a
sustainable growth path.
</P>
<P>
It is estimated that Zimbabwe will receive more than 800
million U.S. dollars from other donor agencies once the IMF
resumes its support. 
