<HEADLINE> UCI Gives Green Light to Virenque </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, June 29 (Xinhua) -- The International Cycling Union (
UCI) Tuesday gave green light on Richard Virenque, whose team were
barred last year from Tour de France for doping, to take part in
this year's race.
</P>
<P>
Virenque was not invited to this year's Tour because organizers
feared that his presence would spoil the race's image and
reputation.
</P>
<P>
The race begins on Monday. 
</P>
