<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, June 29 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 4,676.39 on Tuesday, down 4.58
points, or 0.09 percent, from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover stood at over 84 trillion Turkish Liras (about
202 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 17.51 points, or 0.29 percent, to
close at 6,463.19 points, the industrial index fell 39.93 points,
or 1.32 percent, to close at 3,007.76 points while the services
index rose 63.27 points, or 1.25 percent, to close at 5,136.05
points. 
</P>
