50,000-strong peacekeeping force into Kosovo to flush out Serb
paramilitaries.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at a photo opportunity in his office with Romanian
Defense Minister Victor Babiuc, Cohen said that "There might be
these groups or attempts to disrupt the peace process there."
</P>
<P>
