<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, June 29 (Xinhua) -- French President Jacques Chirac
called on Turkey on Tuesday to commute the verdict on Kurdish
rebel leader Abdullah Ocalan to another penalty rather than
executing him.
</P>
<P>
